# 🍫 Chocolate Sales Dashboard

## Overview

This Power BI dashboard provides an interactive analysis of chocolate sales performance across multiple countries, products, salespeople, and time periods. It enables users to monitor key business metrics, identify sales trends, and make data-driven decisions through dynamic visualisations and KPIs.

